Results.Description: The Schönhauser Allee Arcaden are located in the district of Prenzlauer Berg, centrally located in the main shopping area of the avenue of the same name. With 90 shops on five levels, the shopping centre offers pure shopping pleasure and combines the diverse shopping possibilities with a cosy stop in the gastronomy. If you want to stroll here, you can park at the Schönhauser Allee Arcaden multi-storey car park in Berlin. The entrance to the multi-storey car park is via Greifenhagener Straße. Conveniently located, the multi-storey car park is easy to reach and offers comfortable parking facilities with direct access to the shopping centre. The car park is open daily and offers short and long-term parkers favorable parking rates. It not only offers short distances to the shops in the shopping centre, but also invites you to stroll along Schönhauser Allee.

Results.CarparkLongName: Berlin, Das Center am Potsdamer Platz
Results.Description: The "Das Center am Potsdamer Platz" (aka: Sony Center at Potsdamer Platz) in Berlin is a futuristic building complex, which not only houses residential and working space, but also houses a large film house, an entertainment center, retail stores and restaurants / cafes. APCOA gives you the opportunity to park directly at the "Das Center am Potsdamer Platz" Berlin. You can park your vehicle around the clock at a low price and do your shopping on foot or pursue your leisure activites on site. Not only do you have direct access to the "Das Center am Potsdamer Platz" – Berlin‘s many sights are also nearby and within walking distance of the multi-storey car park: The Tiergarten, Philharmonie and various museums, the Kulturforum and the Potsdamer-Platz-Arkaden. APCOA FLOW customers can also park without ticket and cashless. Long term parking with our season ticket or contract parking is also available.
Results.DescriptionShort: Car park "Das Center am Potsdamer Platz" in Berlin. You park near to Tiergarten, philharmonics and museum, culture forum, Marlene-Dietrich-Platz, Potsdamer-Platz-Arkaden, Brandenburger Tor, Reichstag, the Jewish monument, casino of Berlin, theater at Potsdamer Platz and BLUMAX-theater. In this car park you can rent a parking space or long-term parking. Long-term parking possible.

Results.Description:
Discover Hamburg: Park your car in the Elbphilharmonie Hamburg multi-storey car park and continue your journey on foot from here: the historic port and the modern Hafen City are close by - attractions such as the Customs Museum, Miniatur Wunderland, Hamburg Dungeon and the Speicherstadt warehouse district also invite you to go sightseeing. Enjoy a stroll through Hamburg, visit the Port of Hamburg or venture on a culinary foray through the city - the Elbphilharmonie Hamburg multi-storey car park is a good starting point for a wide range of activities. The Plaza is also directly attached and invites you to enjoy a panoramic view of the Port of Hamburg. The multi-storey car park is open daily and offers a total of 334 parking spaces. 

Contract parking is also possible here: rent a parking space for a fixed monthly price and save yourself the expensive short-term parking fees in Hamburg as a frequent parker. On the basis of a long-term rental contract, you can enter and leave the car park as often as you like.

Parking garage Messe Stuttgart: Parking at the Messe Stuttgart.

An annual 1.27 million visitors, around 20,600 exhibitors from all over the world and 67 events - that is the track record of Messe Stuttgart, which is one of the magnets of attraction in Stuttgart and one of Europe's most modern trade fair and congress centers. Those who come to Stuttgart as trade fair visitors can find their way quickly by car via the A8 or the B27, the trade fair center is directly connected here. Visitors can park directly in the Messe Stuttgart parking garage. A total of 7,300 parking spaces are available for visitors at the trade fair and congress center; together with the parking spaces at the nearby Airport, there are even more than 15,000 parking spaces. Drive comfortably by car to the fairgrounds and enjoy a short walk to the entrances of the Messe Stuttgart or the congress center. With the Messe Stuttgart parking garage, APCOA is your guarantee for parking in the direct vicinity of the event location, in bright and friendly surroundings.

Results.Description:
10 minutes for Kiss & Fly
With its automatic number plate recognition system, the airport has the most modern terminal access road in Germany. This technology enables ticketless parking in the 650 metre long "Kiss & Fly" zone. Cameras recognise the number plate and open the barrier. Drivers have ten minutes free passage time for short parking to drop off passengers. For longer stops, payment is simply made by entering the number plate at the machine.

Results.Description:
The Sonnenhof garage in Munich is centrally located in the city center and is only a few minutes' walk from Munich's pedestrian zone. In the immediate vicinity of the parking garage are the City Cinemas, the German Theater and numerous hotels, stores and restaurants.

Entry to the car park
For security reasons, access from the studio/city cinema is secured with a code lock. The door and the gate at the entrance can be opened via the "2005" + bell symbol (the code can also be found on the parking ticket).

Results.Description:
Parking garage Am Treptower Park 14. You can conveniently pay the parking fees via the APCOA FLOW app or the EasyPark app - without a ticket.

And it's as simple as this:

  • Drive into the parking garage.
  • Download/start the free app for iOS or Android.
  • Select the location "Am Treptower Park 14" and set the desired parking time.
  • Start the parking process and pay automatically

If you want to park longer than previously selected, you can extend your parking time in the app.

Car park Cruise Center Steinwerder in Hamburg. Park directly at the cruise terminal and start your cruise.

Make your cruise from Hamburg start relaxed with parking at Apcoa's Cruise Center Steinwerder. Located just a stone’s throw from the port, this car park is the perfect solution for parking your car close to the departure point. As an added bonus, you can book parking in advance for the best price. An online booking will provide added convenience and peace of mind knowing parking has been sorted on time and won't present any problems as you embark on your cruise journey!
